[41:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'You get a contaminationfree model, which is very rare and valuable. You get a window into how data shapes the model\'s personality. You can actually test it. questions about generalization and'

[41:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'forecasting and discovery, which you can\'t really do with modern AI models cuz they\'re trained on everything already. So, if you\'re into AI research or history or just the weird intersection of these two, talk is one'

